<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="against-prep">against <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'ɡenst, ə'ɡeɪnst/    美 /ə'ɡenst, ə'ɡeɪnst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>反对：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Personally, I’m against the measure of paying students to learn.
就我个人而言，我反对用金钱鼓励学生学习的做法。</p><footer>2010 广东书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>违背；逆：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>against one’s wishes / will</strong>
违背某人的意愿</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This was <strong>against the law</strong> (= illegal).
这是违法的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The ship is sailing against the wind. 
船正在逆风航行。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>和...比赛、对抗等：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ll be competing against some of the best companies in Europe.
我们要和一些一流的欧洲公司竞争。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>倚靠；向着；对着：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He leaned against the door. 
他倚着门。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The rain beat against the windows. 
雨打在窗户上。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>防备；以备：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Squirrels store up food against the winter. 
松鼠贮存食物以备过冬。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.<strong>以...为背景；衬托：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The picture looks good against the white wall. 
在白墙的衬托下这幅画很好看。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It was a real race <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ time to get the project done. Luckily, we made it.   （2013 全国改）  </li>
<li>An agreement seems to be impossible because the majority of the committee members are <strong><em>_</em></strong> (反对) it.  （2012 陕西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. against  2. against  </p></div>